0.1 (2026-04-17)
- Initial release
- Adds RsyncMetricsService: injects rsyncFiles, rsyncBytes, rsyncDuration
  into archive records when record_stats=true is set in [[RSYNC]]
- Automatic archive schema extension on first run
- Staleness guard: injects NULL if no successful upload within 2x archive_interval
- Requires rsyncupload.py patch (record_stats option) — see PR or apply manually
